{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't a pit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But you know when iron ore is smelted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "To tell you what-- how many degrees of heat comes out of that, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, I just don't know these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we were on the same premises, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The-- the-- the cannon stripping was adjacent to that smelting oven, whatever you called it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is where a lot of men died from the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kept dying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Meanwhile, they would ship new people, you see, from other communities because they always kept that certain number, and I really couldn't tell you what number.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But eventually, those two camps were joined.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first camp was Strzelnica, which was the name for a shooting range.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the second was Majowka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eventually, everybody from Strzelnica was sent to Majowka, and that's where I now lived with the two sisters, you see?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our father was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was given a job in a laundry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not with my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father lived in separate barracks with the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This camp was run by-- the highest echelon were the Germans-- the Gestapo, the SS, I don't know who-- with the dogs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And under them were the Ukrainians, in uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Ukrainians were the guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they counted the units and marched the units to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, again, we had three shifts, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the oven was going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the smelting oven was going three-- three shifts a-- a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians were vicious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SIGHS] They were abso-- they were-- I mean, they were trying to outdo the Germans in their cruelty.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the-- and of course, by now, though I was a child, I have learned of certain dangers, you see?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I could already perceive danger.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
